org.hatemile.util.html

Interface HTMLDOMElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, HTMLDOMNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsoupHTMLDOMElement

    public interface HTMLDOMElement
extends HTMLDOMNode, Cloneable
    The HTMLDOMElement interface contains the methods for access of the HTML element.
